section.name: QALab Movers and Shakers
section.p: The report is divided in 2 sections, the "Up" represents a list of increased values for the given statistic types: violations or percentage uncovered for Cobertura. They should be fixed as soon a possible! The "Down" section shows the values that have been reduced (fixed) recently.
